0\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/04\/14165307\/before-hire-kitchen-designer-in-bangalore-verify-references-past-work.jpg\" alt=\"Check credentials prior to finalising Bangalore modular kitchen design\" class=\"wp-image-44414\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/04\/14165307\/before-hire-kitchen-designer-in-bangalore-verify-references-past-work.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/04\/14165307\/before-hire-kitchen-designer-in-bangalore-verify-references-past-work-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/04\/14165307\/before-hire-kitchen-designer-in-bangalore-verify-references-past-work-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/04\/14165307\/before-hire-kitchen-designer-in-bangalore-verify-references-past-work-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">Get a 3-D rendering of your kitchen interiors. <\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Kitchen Interior Design Services In Bangalore<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>You&#8217;ve found a list of great kitchen interior designers in Bangalore. What next? Not all designers offer the same service packages. Whether you need a simple remodelling done or amp up the space with the latest tech, knowing what you&#8217;ll get within your budget is important to consider before hiring designers. Here are some of the most common services that an interior designer must offer:&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li>Consultation&nbsp;<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Site assessment and measurements<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Design concepts and planning&nbsp;<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Purchasing&nbsp;<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Management and final execution<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/04\/14165329\/kitchen-interior-design-services-bangalore.jpg\" alt=\"Designcafe offers quality kitchen interior design service in banglaore\" class=\"wp-image-44417\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/04\/14165329\/kitchen-interior-design-services-bangalore.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/04\/14165329\/kitchen-interior-design-services-bangalore-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/04\/14165329\/kitchen-interior-design-services-bangalore-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/04\/14165329\/kitchen-interior-design-services-bangalore-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">Have a detailed discussion before a final yes.<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Keep An Open Mind When Hiring Kitchen Interior Designers In Bangalore<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Before you delve deeper into the nuances of the project, keep an open mind for any ideas and suggestions you receive from the designers. The best way to hire modular kitchen interior designers in Bangalore is to get an idea of their natural styles. Some prefer neutral colour palettes with wood, while others work with stone and laminates. Before finalising a designer, narrow down options that complement your lifestyle and taste.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/04\/14165342\/tips-for-hiring-kitchen-designers-bangalore-based-on-lifestyle-taste.jpg\" alt=\"Tips for hiring kitchen designers in bangalore based on lifestyle &amp; taste\" class=\"wp-image-44419\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/04\/14165342\/tips-for-hiring-kitchen-designers-bangalore-based-on-lifestyle-taste.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/04\/14165342\/tips-for-hiring-kitchen-designers-bangalore-based-on-lifestyle-taste-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/04\/14165342\/tips-for-hiring-kitchen-designers-bangalore-based-on-lifestyle-taste-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/04\/14165342\/tips-for-hiring-kitchen-designers-bangalore-based-on-lifestyle-taste-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">Hire designers who maximise space in your home.<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">FAQs on Kitchen Interior Designers In Bangalore<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>How much does an interior designer charge in Bangalore?<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Several factors determine the <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/home-interiors\/interior-design-cost-in-bangalore\/\">cost of an interior designer in Bangalore<\/a>. On average, designing a 1 BHK between 500 to 550 sq. feet costs anywhere between 4 lakhs to 6 lakhs. It goes up to 9 lakhs for a 2 BHK and 15 lakhs for a 3 BHK.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>How much does an interior designer charge for a kitchen remodel?<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Remodelling costs depend on the layout of the kitchen and the materials used. Here is an estimate:&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li>L-shaped: INR 3000- 4200\/ sq. ft<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Straight: INR 600- 2250\/ sq. ft<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Parallel: INR 1200- 1750\/ sq. ft<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>U-shaped: INR 225<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n\n\n\n<p>Material Cost:<\/p>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li>Wood: INR 300- 800\/ sq. ft<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>PVC- INR 200- 2200\/ sq. ft&nbsp;<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Stainless Steel- INR 200- 5500\/ sq. ft<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>How do I choose a kitchen designer?<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Consider these tips when choosing a kitchen designer:&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li>Design and creative abilities&nbsp;<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Technical capabilities&nbsp;<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Product knowledge<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Experience&nbsp;<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Communication skills&nbsp;<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Credentials&nbsp;<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>What are the 6 types of kitchen layouts?<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>The 6 most popular <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/guides\/different-types-of-kitchen-layouts\/\">types of kitchen layouts<\/a> are:&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li>L-Shaped&nbsp;<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>U-Shaped&nbsp;<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Island Kitchen&nbsp;<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Peninsula Kitchen&nbsp;<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>G- Shaped Kitchen&nbsp;<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>One Wall Kitchen&nbsp;<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n\n\n\n<p>Still confused about finding the best kitchen interior designers in Bangalore? <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/\">DesignCafe<\/a> has got your back. Skip the tedious process of searching and verifying, and contact our design experts for a hassle-free home designing experience.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"row blog-form\">\n\t<div class=\"offset-lg-3 col-lg-6 bg-light\">\n<fieldset class=\"field-set\">\n<!-- <legend align=\"left\"> -->\n                    \n    <h3 class=\"widget-title text-dark text-center mb-0\">Looking For Modular Kitchens At Best Prices<\/h3>\n  \n \n     <p class=\"text-center text-dark mt-0\"> Speak to our kitchen experts today!<\/p>\n    <!-- <\/legend> -->\n<form id=\"blogContactUsFormMain\" action=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/get_quote_action.php\" method=\"post\"\n    novalidate=\"novalidate\">\n    <div class=\"form-group\">\n        <input type=\"text\" class=\"form-control\"  name=\"your-name\" placeholder=\"Enter your name*\" \/>\n        <!-- <span class=\"sales-txt-label\" id=\"labeltxt\">Enter your name*<\/span>  -->\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"form-row dc-falg-row\">\n        <!-- <div class=\"form-group col-md-3 guideForm\">\n            <select name=\"your-phone-ext\" id=\"id_select2_examp